divs: Sighting Detailsblinking flashing rotating red blue wnd white light to side no movement across horizon.. I was walking friends out and just looking up in the sky we noticed the lights my friend got out a pair of binoculars I looked first then he asked if I had a camera to catch some video the objects were in the sw sky and kept flashing different color light red blue white rotating not moving like any fixed wing aircraft staying fixed in the sky also air traffic none in the area usually flight path for john wayne I grew up Air Force brat and seen lots of planes helecopters but this just is'nt right and after 20 min I just got tired and went in
Summary: Lights flashing in sw sky caught eyes walking friends out.
